data.title: Amy LeSlie and James Henry - Marriage Records
data.meta_description: Ancestry.ca has at least 1 marriage record for Amy LeSlie and James Henry, among more than 1025 marriage records for the surname LeSlie and more than 2776 marriage records for the surname Henry.
data.text:
Ancestry.ca, the largest online family history resource, can help you explore marriage records for Amy LeSlie and James Henry from among its billions of historical records from Canada and around the world.

Marriage records are primary resources for the marriage details, since they were created at the time of the marriage. Ancestry.ca collections include indexes that can help you request the record, and in some cases, actual images of the marriage records.
